1.6  Five-year Accident History

Minnesota Refining Division maintains a 5-year accident history that fulfills the requirements of the RMP rule.  This history indicates a good record of accidental release prevention over the past 5 years.  No releases of RMP regulated substances have occurred from Minnesota Refining Division within the last 5 years that have resulted in offsite consequences.  The following release at Minnesota Refining Division within the past 5 years did result in onsite consequences:

